#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:203
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Synchronize all existing events`: sync all events on *Google "
"Calendar* and/or Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`同步所有現有活動`：同步\\ *Google Calendar*\\ 和/或 Odoo 日曆上的"
"所有活動。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:206
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:252
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` after making the selection to modify the user's "
"events and the calendar synchronization."
msgstr "完成選擇後按一下\\ :guilabel:`確認`\\ 以修改使用者的活動和日曆同步。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:210
