":icon:`oi-smile-add`\\ :guilabel:`（加入反應）`\\ 圖示，然後選擇所需的表情符"
"號。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/share_collaborate.rst:215
msgid "View comments"
msgstr "檢視註解"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/share_collaborate.rst:217
msgid ""
"When a comment has been added to a cell, a small yellow triangle appears in "
"the top right corner of the cell."
msgstr "當註解已加入到儲存格時，儲存格的右上角會出現一個小黃色三角形。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/share_collaborate.rst:220
msgid ""
"To view a comment thread on a single cell, hover over the cell; click the "
"cell or the comment thread to open the thread to be able to add a comment."
msgstr ""
