"下拉式選單中選擇所需客服人員的姓名，並按一下\\ :guilabel:`連線`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:94
msgid ""
"To manually log a dynamic agent out of a call queue, navigate to the `Axivox "
"management console <https://manage.axivox.com>`_, and "
"click :guilabel:`Queues` from the left-hand menu. Then, click the "
"green :guilabel:`Refresh` button at the top of the :guilabel:`Connected "
"agents` column. From here, click the red :guilabel:`Disconnect` button, and "
"they are immediately disconnected. This can be helpful in situations where "
"agents forget to log out at the end of the day."
msgstr ""
"若要手動將動態客服人員登出通話隊列，請前往\\ `Axivox 管理主控台<https://"
"manage.axivox.com>`_\\ ，並從左側選單中按一下\\ :guilabel:`隊列`\\ 。然後，按"
"一下\\ :guilabel:`已連線的客服人員`\\ 欄位頂端的綠色\\ :guilabel:`重新整理`\\"
" 按鈕。接著，按一下紅色的\\ :guilabel:`中斷連線`\\ 按鈕，他們就會立即中斷連線"
"。這在客服人員忘記在一天結束時登出的情況下很有幫助。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:None
msgid ""
"Call queue with connected agents column highlighted and connect an agent and "
"report buttons\n"
"highlighted."
msgstr "通話隊列，已連線的客服人員欄位已醒目提示，連線客服人員和報表按鈕已醒目提示。"

